{"tid":2218728,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍絲愛股中芯國際仆街了] 美國政府內部文件直指禁售令制裁中芯國際勢在必行","createTime":"2020-09-26T12:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T12:57:50.000Z","uid":108201,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d39bf51e2fb81faf6154e016ea155d773ad5c881","tid":2218728,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:13:47.000Z","msg":"文件指出，2020 年 4 月美國政府制裁中國華為新修訂頒布的第 744.21 節出口管制規定，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">擴大對軍事最終用途和軍事最終用戶限制，並廢除部分管制項目當前適用的民用最終用戶許可證例</span></span></strong>，擬嚴格限制管制物項再出口的許可證例外範圍。法令重點就是在防止中國、俄羅斯和委內瑞拉等國家透過民用供應鏈，或用民用供應鏈取得發展武器、軍用航空器或監視技術的美國相關科技與設備，使用到軍事和軍事最終用戶。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>現在這項規定，也準備套用到中芯國際及集團子公司。</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMMvwDp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMMvwDp.jpg&h=1127e4f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點在<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">將軍事最終用途的定義擴展到「使用」、「開發」或「生產」以外任何計畫</span></strong></span>，包括運輸、安裝、保養、維修、大修、翻新軍事產品與科技等。美國商務部還提出產品和技術的出口管制條例修正案，增加數十種可用於軍事目的的新產品。這些產品出口到俄羅斯、中國和委內瑞拉時，必須向美國當局取得特別許可證。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z1MO2LQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ1MO2LQ.png&h=21a09313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國何時會頒布新制裁令，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">市場預估將是美國大選越來越近，選情越來越緊繃的時候，可能大選前的關鍵時刻就會頒布</span></strong></span>，屆時對全球半導體產業勢必掀起新一波漣漪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/09/26/sanctions-smic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F09%2F26%2Fsanctions-smic%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu4nMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=182bcd7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/09/26/sanctions-smic/</a>"},{"pid":"efba84250f484cb60578a02bac626c294e8db8ad","tid":2218728,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:15:46.000Z","msg":"支足：好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5739056ee6f2789d49b896ca482d53f21d6f06","tid":2218728,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efba84250f484cb60578a02bac626c294e8db8ad","tid":2218728,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:15:46.000Z","msg":"支足：好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:20:57.000Z","msg":"佢哋40蚊接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc697d1dac6c34922c964784590c36b5bcedf1b","tid":2218728,"uid":92401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"正股驚閪<br />\nSH<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下"},{"pid":"ec86ca4de32eddd32f18242373f16f0e9d97520f","tid":2218728,"uid":169071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"原來高通做開賣國賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得制裁華為會出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bed031523c797d2bebce89d91c9d5b5fc45b080","tid":2218728,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dcc697d1dac6c34922c964784590c36b5bcedf1b","tid":2218728,"uid":92401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"正股驚閪<br />\nSH<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"你愛國家，國家愛你嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n準備好drop to zero未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066f421878f168224d169b267134d92ab976e18b","tid":2218728,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec86ca4de32eddd32f18242373f16f0e9d97520f","tid":2218728,"uid":169071,"lik